BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Davis Farmers Market – Year-Round Fresh & Local in Central Park 
 (50th Anniversary Year!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260325T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260325T180000
UID:10000236-1774450800-1774461600@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 50 years of community and bounty at the Davis Farmer
 s Market in 2026! This iconic\, award-winning market is the heartbeat of D
 avis – bringing together local farmers\, artisans\, bakers\, food vendor
 s\, and makers every week. \n\nWednesdays: 3:00 PM – 6:00 PM (September
 –March)\; 4:00 PM – 8:00 PM Picnic in the Park with live music (April
 –August)\n\nShop the freshest seasonal produce\, farm-fresh eggs/meats/c
 heese\, artisan crafts\, hot prepared foods\, coffee\, baked goods\, and m
 ore! All grown or made right here in our region. Enjoy live music (especia
 lly during summer Picnic in the Park Wednesdays)\, family activities\, SNA
 P matching programs\, and the lively downtown energy that makes it a favor
 ite gathering spot for residents\, UC Davis students\, families\, and visi
 tors. \nFree entry – bring your bags and support local agriculture\, sus
 tainability\, and small businesses! Rain or shine\, it’s always a great 
 day out. \nSpecial 2026 highlights: 50th anniversary celebrations througho
 ut the year. Don’t miss the big community event on August 1!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year/2026-03-25/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Downtown at Dusk – Live Music & Evening Vibes on G Street
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260402T200000
UID:10000500-1775152800-1775160000@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Kick off warmer evenings with Downtown at Dusk\, a free series
  co-hosted by Davis Downtown and DRC! Every listed Thursday at 6 PM\, enjo
 y live music\, delicious food from local spots\, good company\, and the li
 vely energy of downtown Davis. Perfect for unwinding after work\, meeting 
 friends\, or a casual date night. Bring blankets or chairs for relaxed vib
 es. \nSupport local musicians\, eateries\, and businesses while soaking in
  spring’s longer days. No tickets needed – just show up! \nDate/Time: 
 Thursdays at 6:00 PM (April 2\, April 9\, April 23\, April 30\, May 7\, Ma
 y 21\, May 28\, June 4\, June 11\, June 18) \nLocation: G Street platform
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/downtown-at-dusk-live-music-evening-vi
 bes-on-g-street/2026-04-02/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Frenzy Coffee 1st Birthday Celebration – Live DJ & Vendors
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260403T173000
UID:10000510-1775210400-1775237400@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Help Frenzy Coffee celebrate their 1st full year in Davis! \nC
 ome join the fun at this all-day birthday party featuring live DJ sets and
  a variety of local vendors. Whether you’re grabbing your morning coffee
 \, stopping by for lunch\, or hanging out in the afternoon\, there will be
  great music\, good vibes\, and plenty of ways to celebrate with the commu
 nity. \nBring your friends\, family\, or coworkers and enjoy the lively at
 mosphere right in the heart of downtown Davis. Everyone is welcome! \nFree
  to attend – no tickets needed. Just stop by\, enjoy the music\, shop lo
 cal vendors\, and help celebrate one year of Frenzy Coffee! \nDate/Time: F
 riday\, April 3\, 2026 | 10:00 AM – 5:30 PM \nLocation: Frenzy Coffee\, 
 305 1st Street\, Downtown Davis
LOCATION:Frenzy Coffee\, 305 1st St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/frenzy-coffee-1st-birthday-celebration
 -live-dj-vendors/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Day in Downtown – Vendor Market & Street Celebration (Free!)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260405T160000
UID:10000496-1775383200-1775404800@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Spend a full day exploring Day in Downtown – a vibrant\, fre
 e street event bringing together local talent and community! From 10 AM to
  4 PM\, browse a diverse lineup of vendors on E Street (between 3rd & 4th 
 St.)\, including: \n\nVintage clothing & unique finds\nLocal artists\, mak
 ers\, and creators\nDavis brick-and-mortar shops\nNon-profits sharing thei
 r work\nSpecial spots like Sophia’s Thai Kitchen for tasty bites\n\nDisc
 over one-of-a-kind items\, support small businesses and local organization
 s\, and enjoy the lively energy of downtown Davis. Perfect for a relaxed S
 unday outing with friends\, family\, or solo shopping. Bring reusable bags
  and comfy shoes!
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/day-in-downtown-vendor-market-street-c
 elebration-free/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Picnic in the Park at Davis Farmers Market – Wednesday Evenings 
 (50th Anniversary Year)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T200000
UID:10000512-1775664000-1775678400@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:The beloved Picnic in the Park season is back at the Davis Far
 mers Market starting Wednesday\, April 1\, 2026! \nEvery Wednesday evening
  through August 26\, the market expands to 4:00 – 8:00 PM\, turning Cent
 ral Park into the perfect spot for a relaxed picnic dinner. Shop fresh pro
 duce\, artisan goods\, and a wide variety of prepared foods from your favo
 rite vendors. Enjoy local craft beer\, wine\, and brand new this year – 
 mead! \nEach week features live music and children’s activities\, creati
 ng a festive\, family-friendly atmosphere. Bring blankets\, lawn chairs\, 
 and reusable bags. It’s the ideal way to unwind\, connect with neighbors
 \, and support local farmers and food makers. \nThis year is extra special
  as the Davis Farmers Market celebrates its 50th Anniversary! Don’t miss
  the big anniversary celebration on Saturday\, August 1\, 2026. \nNew in 2
 026: The Market Memories Cookbook (presale now at davis-farmers-market). \
 nHighlights Include: \n\nBuckhorn Food Truck\, The Hotdogger\, Dhillon Far
 m\, Davis Bread & Desserts\, Greek Table\, Kettle Pop & more\nLive music e
 very week\nKids’ activities\nLocal beer\, wine & mead\n\nFree to attend 
 – everyone is welcome!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year-2/2026-04-08/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Davis Downtown Board Meeting
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T100000
UID:10000014-1775725200-1775728800@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the second Thursday of each month for our Governing
  Board of Directors meeting. The meeting is open to all interested. Stay u
 p-to-date on business and initiatives related to downtown Davis\, and the 
 opportunity to provide public comment will be available. \nMeetings are cu
 rrently held virtually on the Zoom platform from 9:00am to 10:00am. If you
  are interested in attending\, please contact us at info@davisdowntown.com
  to request a Zoom meeting invitation. \nTo view\, download and/or print B
 oard of Directors meeting agendas or minutes\, click on the following link
 : https://davisdowntown.com/agendas-meeting-information. \nMeeting locatio
 ns and times are subject to change.
LOCATION:Davis Downtown Board Meeting\, Zoom\, Davis\, CA
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-downtown-board-meeting/2026-04-0
 9/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
